<br>
&quot;We shall see what is written soon enough dear Nephew. You may be the King of the Gods, but to us, you are still a mere boy.&quot;<br>
<br>
The three sisters looked to Alysia before she left.<br>
<br>
&quot;Dear sister, blessings to you and your husband. May any who tries to harm such, be cursed with oblivion.&quot;<br>
<br>
They then bowed in respect to Hera and the others as they vanished in a whirl of flames. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uzeuskingofthegods.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zeus King of the Gods</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/17/01 8:55:22 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: With a growl</span><hr size=1> Zeus glared at the furies and with a simple statement reminded them that the only reason they remain on Olympus is because he allows it, &quot;Do not forget dear old ladies the fate of the Titans and wherein your own fate could very well be.&quot;  <br>
<br>
He then watched his eyes narrowed as they disappeared.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 16<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/17/01 9:15:56 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: She laughed. . .</span><hr size=1> ::Poseidon continues to stare at Zeus the whole time and shakes his head in disgust.::<br>
<br>
&quot;I am above this sort of treatment brother. If anyone is the girl here it is you. Whinning about this and that. Let us gods have some space will you? You say it is written that you are fair, it is also written that Apollo is all- good. He didn't seem too good to me when he flayed Marsyas, though justly so. You make bad choices at times my brother and I'm not the only god to have noticed them. Calm yourself now my brother and heed my words who am your elder.&quot;<br>
<br>
::Looks to Apollo:: <br>
<br>
&quot;I didn't mean to disrespect you nephew, it was just to make a point.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uzeuskingofthegods.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zeus King of the Gods</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/18/01 10:11:25 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Anger Unsheathed</span><hr size=1> The face of the king of the gods turned red, his anger all encompassing at this point.  His voice boomed above the heavens and the temples to the sea god shook.  &quot;I will not be talked to in that manner in my own realm.&quot; <br>
<br>
He launched a lightning bolt at his brother.  &quot;You return  to your own realm and do not set foot on Olympus until such time as I see fit.  Perhaps you forget the consequences of an attempt to overthrow the King of the Gods?&quot;  His now dark eyes turn to Hera.  &quot;Mayhaps the Queen would like to remind you of what occurs as a result of your insolence.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/utheerinyes.showPublicProfile?language=EN>The Erinyes</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 46<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/18/01 2:27:19 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Comming Back. . </span><hr size=1> They returned looking at their nephew. It was obvious Tisiphone was the one to bring her sisters back. She loved her family. . . as much as a Furie can love of course. She was the Goddess of Vengence but for some reason her heart held a place for each of them. <br>
<br>
She remembered how it felt to each of her sisters when their own siblings were put away for all time. And she missed them.<br>
<br>
She nudged Alecto and Megaera towards Zeus.<br>
<br>
Alecot sighed and looked to Hera seeing Zeus glare at his own wife. &quot;We would like to apologise for our harsh words Nephew. The well-being of Olympus is in our hands as much as anyone else.&quot;<br>
<br>
Megaera nodded and for the first time, she spoke without a smirk on her face. &quot;We respect your place as King of the Gods, but you must understand the position we hold. For we were born long before the Olympians and I suppose we are still holding grudges deep inside for the loss of our own family.&quot;<br>
<br>
Tisiphone smiled lightly and looked at Hera.<br>
 <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uqueenhera.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Queen Hera</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen of the Gods</span><br>  Posts: 59<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/18/01 5:16:47 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Enough</span><hr size=1> &quot;Enough!&quot; came the voice sitting alone on her throne.  &quot;This bickering if foolish.  We have been here before...our power struggles being old,&quot; Hera arose from her seat and walked towards the bickering Olympians. &quot;But, now the times have changed.  There are other's who want to end our reigns...on Olympus, in the Seas, and in the Underworld,&quot; her eyes narrowed at them all.  &quot;We have enough enemies, without destorying each other ourselves.  Poseidon... is King of the Seas...and respected there.  Hades is King of the Underworld, and respected there.  Zeus.. is King of the Lands, Mortals, and Land dwelling beasts.  And by rights.. King of the Gods.  Let's not step on those old paths right now.  Even Poseidon has recently felt someone's attempt on his life, just the other day.  So.. I say ENOUGH.  We have enough to take care of and worry about.&quot;  She moved slowely over to Zeus and gently put a hand upon his arm and smiled. &quot;I thank you dear for bringing your siblings back from our father's stomach.  And yes, you are King.  Now...let us end this nonsense.&quot; <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#336699><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uzeuskingofthegods.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Zeus King of the Gods</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Moderator</span><br>  Posts: 23<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/18/01 10:58:23 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enough</span><hr size=1> Zeus nods, his gaze softening as Hera touches him.  He nods to the Furies, &quot;The Olympians are your family now.&quot;  His voice was much softer now and there wasn't a boom to be heard, &quot;Of course my dear, you are right, enough.&quot;  He pulled his wife into his arms and hugged her.  &quot;My apologies for losing my temper as such.&quot;<br>
<br>
He frowned slightly and then moved to settle onto his throne.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#003366><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uposeidonkofc.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Poseidonkofc</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>registered user</span><br>  Posts: 19<br> <font color=#FFFF33>(5/19/01 3:14:30 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Enough</span><hr size=1> :<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :p --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/tongue.gif ALT=":p"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> oesidon gets up and slowly walks away from the company with his head down in sorrow.::<br>
